name: 2023 7th International Conference on Medical and Health Informatics
content: ICMHI 2023 publication information: Accepted papers of ICMHI 2023 will be published in International Conference Proceedings Series by ACM (ISBN: 979-8-4007-0071-2), which will be sent to Ei Compendex and Scopus for indexing, and submitted to be reviewed by Thomson Reuters Conference Proceedings Citation Index (ISI Web of Science).
